User Stories:

As a player, I want to be able to save my character in the event that I have to stop playing because I do not
want to start over every time I play the game.

As a player, I want to load a character so that I may resume where I left off in case I had to stop playing.

As a player, I want to be able to delete a character in case I do not want that character anymore.

As a player, I want to view the leaderboard so that I can brag to my friends if I have a higher score than them.

As a player, I want to be able to play the game because it will be a good way for me to entertain myself when
I have free time.

As a player, I want the game to update the leaderboard so that others can see if I move up a rank.

As a player, I want to earn experience so that I can level up and achieve a higher score.

As a player, I want to increase skills so that I can complete levels quicker and with more money so that I can be
a higher rank.

As a player, I want to be able to challenge a specific player so that I can show them who's the boss!

As a player, I want to be able to see score of a specific player in case I'm competing against him/her.

As a player, I want to be able to quit the game anytime I want so that I can go attend other things.
